room_title: Escape room "The Lost City" by Last Minute Escape in New York
review: We did The Lost City a week ago. It was awesome! They really kept with the theme, and the puzzles were really thought-provoking. This might have been my favorite room yet! Next up is the submarine!

room_title: Escape room "The Lost City" by Last Minute Escape in New York
review: Best escape room yet. Love all their rooms. Challenging, fun, and the themes keep it interesting. Looking forward to their next.

room_title: Escape room "The Lost City" by Last Minute Escape in New York
review: This was one of the best experiences we had! We would definitely do it again! The staff was really friendly and funny as well!

room_title: Escape room "The Lost City" by Last Minute Escape in New York
review: I have done multiple rooms with Last Minute Escape and continue to come back. It is a great event and so much fun. The time flies and it is over before you know it. I absolutely recommend!!!
